com.facebook.buck.core.artifact

Interface BuildArtifact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Artifact, SkylarkArtifactApi, com.google.devtools.build.lib.skylarkinterface.SkylarkPrintable, com.google.devtools.build.lib.skylarkinterface.SkylarkValue

    public interface BuildArtifact
extends Artifact
    Represents an Artifact that is materialized by an Action.

    This is not intended to be exposed to users, but used only by the build engine.
